# Accessing Google Drive from Python

Chat with GPT: https://chat.openai.com/share/dadb0434-9fb0-4b9f-8e89-d9e5ce391d3b

Prerequisites: 
- [[Google Cloud Console account]], 
- [[GCP Project]]
  
Steps:
- Enable [[Google Drive API]]
- Generate [[Google API Key]]
- Add the Key
  - o1: Add to [[Env Variables]]
  - o2: Add to [[Secrets Storage]]
  - o3: Add to [[.env]], `load_dotenv()`
- Install PyDrive lib
    - O1: `pip install PyDrive`
    - O2: add to pyproject.toml, `poetry update`
